sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as User
participant Client as WebClient
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant AuthSvc as AuthService
participant UserAuthDb as MongoUserAuth
participant UserSvc as UserService

Note over User,UserSvc: Luong 2 - Verify email + bootstrap profile
User->>Client: Bam link verify tu email
Client->>Gateway: GET /api/auth/verify-email?token=...
Gateway->>AuthSvc: Forward verify token
AuthSvc->>UserAuthDb: Check token + set isActive/isEmailVerified
alt Token hop le
  AuthSvc->>UserSvc: Bootstrap profile noi bo
  AuthSvc-->>Gateway: 200 verified
  Gateway-->>Client: Tai khoan san sang dang nhap
else Token sai/het han
  AuthSvc-->>Gateway: 400/410
  Gateway-->>Client: Verify that bai
end
